article.description: — Tyler Burton had 26 points as Richmond defeated Northern Iowa 60-52 on Sunday.
article.headline: Burton scores 26 to carry Richmond over Northern Iowa 60-52
article.linkText: Burton scores 26 to carry Richmond over Northern Iowa 60-52
article.story: CEDAR FALLS, Iowa -- — Tyler Burton had 26 points as Richmond defeated Northern Iowa 60-52 on Sunday. Grant Golden had seven rebounds for the Spiders (5-4). Nick Sherod added eight rebounds. Noah Carter had 13 points for the Panthers (2-5). AJ Green added nine rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
